# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>The Word of Blake Militia inherited ComStar's combined-arms organizational philosophy and its Star League-era equipment stocks, fielding infantry formations that ranked among the best equipped in the Inner Sphere during the Jihad. Crewing rotary autocannon that can sustain extraordinary rates of fire, these gunners lay down suppressive barrages that saturate an area with projectiles, trading accuracy and weapon longevity for sheer volume of fire.</p>
</overview>

